      About this item

      • One-hand Operation: UGREEN car phone holder for air vent enables you to put down or pick up your phone simply with one hand. Just clip this car phone mount onto the air vent and slip your phone into its gravity clamp. The gravity phone holder not only keeps your phone close to you for easy access and hands-free navigation, but also won't block your driving vision.
      • Hold Your Phone Securely: Lock your phone automatically and grip it firmly, free your hand for safe driving. The gravity car vent phone holder features an auto-clamp gravity holder to hold your phone in place. Simply put your phone into the gravity holder, the gravity will retract the holder's arms and form a stable triangle structure to securely hold your phone, even on speed humps or bumpy road.
      • Friendly Design: The gravity iPhone vent mount features soft silicone pads on its gravity holder arms and clips to protect your phone and car air vent from scratch primely. The reserved charging port enables you to charge your phone and keep it on power even on this gravity mount. Never worry about power off on your trip when this car mount is installed.
      • Durable with Premium Quality: The gravity air vent car phone mount features durable and elegant aluminum alloy holder arms, easy to fit your phone and no need to clamp the phone with 2 hands. Simply insert the air vent phone holder into the vent to complete the installation, the soft rubber grip clamps the vent firmly and well protecting your vent blades from scratches.
      • Universal Fit: Support 4.7" to 7" phone with thickness up to 0.4 inches (including the phone case), compatible for iPhone 12 11 Pro Max, new iPhone SE, iPhone XS XR X 8 Plus 7 6 6s, Samsung Galaxy Note20 S20 Ultra S10 Plus S10e S9+ S9 S8 Note 9 8 S7 S6 Edge, LG V20 V30 V40 V10 K10 G4 G5 G6 G7 G8 ThinQ, Google Pixel 4, Pixel 2 XL, Pixel 3 3a XL, Nexus 5X 6P, OnePlus 7T 7 6T 6 5T 5 3T 3, Motorola Razr 2019, Moto G7 G6 E4 E5, Moto Z Force, etc.

      Product Description

      Free Your Hands for Safe Driving

      Designed with unique gravity linkage arms, UGREEN portable air vent mount allows you to simply lock and ease cell phone automatically in place by one hand. Durable holder arm with soft silicone pad, securely hold your phone and protect it from scratch.

      Tool-Free Installation, Easy to Handle

      UGREEN car holder for vent ensures you easy mounting by one hand in few seconds. Simply clip it to the car air vent, then put down your smartphone straightly in its bracket, the cradle will auto-lock by gravity securely.

      Hold Your Phone Securely

      With gravity linkage design, UGREEN vent phone holder's arms can form a stable triangle structure when you place the phone on. Hold your phone securely even on a bumpy road.

      Metal arms for Durable and Firmly

      High-quality aluminum alloy metal arms form a more stable triangle structure and bring more steady power to hold your phone while driving, providing a longer lifespan.

      Kindly Reminder

      It is suggested to apply this car phone mount only to horizontal car vent blades for a more secure grip. This car vent mount cannot work on those cars with arc-shaped, retraction type, non-intensive, round, or other irregular air vents.

      Fit for 4.7inch to Max 7 inches Phone

      This gravity linkage phone holder only fits for the phone screen size up to 6.5-inch, thickness up to 0.4 inch (including the phone case), and can only hold up to 7.34 ounces weight.

      • Compatible for Apple iPhone 12 Pro Max 12 Mini, iPhone 11 Pro Max, iPhone XR X X Max ,iPhone 8, 8 plus, 7 ,7 plus, 6, 6 plus, 6s, 6s plus;

      • Compatible for Google Pixel XL, pixel 2 3 xl, google pixel 3a, Nexus 5X 6P, OnePlus 6T 6 5T 5 3T 3 2;

      • Compatible for Motorola Moto G7 G6 E4 E5 Z3, Z2 Play, Moto Z, Z Force, Sony Xperia R1 plus, XZ XZ1 XZ2 XZ3 XA XA1 Z3 Z5;
      • Compatible for HTC 10, U12+, One M9, Xiaomi Redmi Note 5, Mi 6, Mi 5;
      • Compatible for Huawei P20, P20 Pro, P20 Lite, P10, P10+, P10 Lite, P9, P9+, P9 Lite, P8, P8 Lite, Mate 10 Pro, Mate 9 Pro, Mate 8, Honor 10 9 8.

      Textured silicone pads inside the clamping cradle help hold your iPhone tightly, protecting your phone from scratches.

      With sturdy clips, this car mount allows you to clip to your air vents firmly, no worry about falling off even on a bumpy road.

      Reserved charging port design allows you to insert charging cable directly to the smartphone without blocking.

          Deana Taylor
          4.0 out of 5 stars Not what I was expecting, but it works
          Reviewed in the United States on May 22, 2019
          Verified Purchase
          When I bought this, I thought it was a suction type, but it is not. It slides onto the vent itself, and that blocks one of the vents, which sucks, but I can deal with that when I need to. I just remove the holder when I am not using it.

          The description also says that it hold most phones, all the way up to the latest iPhone, but it doesn't state that you shouldn't use a case on your phone when it is in the cradle. I have a One Plus 5T, and with the case, it barely fits width wise, and it doesn't sit in the bottom cradle, it just kind of rests on top. I think if I took it out of the case it might barely fit, but there is no chance it will hold an iPhone 10 or one of those phones that looks like a small tablet.

          I know that a lot of that sounds negative, and my original review was only 2 stars, but their customer service was on the ball when they saw I was unhappy with the product. That earned them another star. And, when I look at the holder, I can tell that it is made well. The arms are metal, it has a soft foam lining so it won't scratch your phone, the clip part is sturdy and hold well. It doesn't bounce around on the vent. And, it is rotatable so you can mount your phone horizontally of vertically without having to remove it from the holder or the vent. The quality construction rated it another star as well. I would recommend a deeper cradle design that will accommodate cases, but all in all it is a product that I use regularly, and I am not looking for a replacement any time soon.

          M. Gardner
          3.0 out of 5 stars Not bad, not great either
          Reviewed in the United Kingdom on October 14, 2019
          Verified Purchase
          For a cheap clip-on phone holder, this works absolutely fine. It clips onto the slats on your dashboard fan, which does limit placement a little bit. The arms of the cradle use the weight of the device itself to ensure a snug fit. I actually use a 6-inch+ Black Shark 2, which is fairly oversized and rather heavy, and it just about copes with that. With that in mind, it'll deal with most large smartphones (e.g. iPhone XS Max, OnePlus 7 Pro, Pixel 3 XL) fairly well.

          It's not the most stable piece of kit, though, and you'll get some wobble. I've not had it detach while in motion, even when braking hard, which is a good sign. But it's not going to win any awards for sturdiness any time soon.

          To be fair, it doesn't really pretend to be anything that its not. If you want a phone holder for your car, but don't fancy obscuring part of your windscreen, this is a decent, if unspectacular option that'll do the job.

          It means, that it will only hold the phone if the bottom hook it pulled down by the weight of your phone. This means :

          - if you tilt the phone sideways, the side hook pulls open the hold ... and your phone goes flying
          - Because of the mechanism, the bigger your phone eg Iphone XR the higher up the phone it will be held .... and there is a potential for your phone to go flying.
